 * Content is migrated 1:1 from /solutions/multifamily.astro so
 * the new design can be evaluated against the same source data.
 * Once the template is approved here it'll be rolled out across
 * the rest of the service slugs.
 *
 * The whole page is just data + a single component. Future
 * design tweaks happen in ServicePageV2.astro and propagate to
 * every service that uses it.
 */
